  <entry>
    <title>Hexo NexT配置说明</title>
    <link href="https://longfeihao.github.io/2020/05/16/hexo-config/"/>
    <id>https://longfeihao.github.io/2020/05/16/hexo-config/</id>
    <published>2020-05-15T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-05-16T05:07:38.278Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h1><p>Git, nodejs<br>参考: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs安装</a></p><p>安装nodejs包：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g  hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-filter-mathjax</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo博客搭建"><a href="#hexo博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="hexo博客搭建"></a>hexo博客搭建</h2><p>初始化：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设定主题为NexT<br>参考: <a href="https://theme-next.iissnan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NexT</a></p><h2 id="知乎微博等自定义图标"><a href="#知乎微博等自定义图标" class="headerlink" title="知乎微博等自定义图标"></a>知乎微博等自定义图标</h2><p>参考: <a href="https://blog.dlzhang.com/posts/32/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">图标问题</a></p><h2 id="一些配置细节"><a href="#一些配置细节" class="headerlink" title="一些配置细节"></a>一些配置细节</h2><p>一共两个配置文件，都是<code>_config.yaml</code>。分别称为主配置文件和主题配置文件。细节可根据说明配置。</p><h3 id="评论系统"><a href="#评论系统" class="headerlink" title="评论系统"></a>评论系统</h3><p>比较简单的一个是valine,详细配置可参考<br><a href="https://qianfanguojin.github.io/2019/07/23/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BANext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0Valine%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">valine配置</a></p><h3 id="标签云"><a href="#标签云" class="headerlink" title="标签云"></a>标签云</h3><p>如果想tag安装文字云的形式展示，可参考<a href="https://github.com/MikeCoder/hexo-tag-cloud" target="_blank" rel="noopener">tagcloud</a></p><h3 id="其他配置"><a href="#其他配置" class="headerlink" title="其他配置"></a>其他配置</h3><p>如相册，广告等设置可参考<a href="https://www.qtmuniao.com/2019/10/16/hexo-theme-landscaping/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">其他配置</a></p><h2 id="发布到github上"><a href="#发布到github上" class="headerlink" title="发布到github上"></a>发布到github上</h2><p>参考: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment" target="_blank" rel="noopener">deploy</a></p><h2 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h2><p>本地部署: <code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</code><br>博客部署: <code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</code><br>新建博客: <code>hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code></p><p>参考: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/writing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写作</a></p>]]></content>
    
